The Amiga Information Online Compilation CD is due for release
early April. This is a {bold}limited edition{nobold} CD and will be
sold on a first come first served basis, a limited amount of
copies are being made and so pre-order now to avoid missing out.
{pp}
The expected release date is : {bold}1st April 2002{nobold}.
{pp}
The CD contains every issue of AIO ever made from 1997-2002. It
will also include a SPECIAL issue, Issue 57 which is {bold}EXCLUSIVE{nobold} to
the CD and cannot be seen anywhere else, it will not be available
to download.
{pp}
Aswell as that, the CD includes a host of essential guides by our
very own Peter Hutchison. To fill the CD out, the bigger Aminet
downloads will be included like the English Amiga report from the
Amiga 2001 show held in Germany in MPEG video format. Other
big downloads like Payback and Genetic Species will be included
so you dont have to download these. Some are over 100mb!
{pp}
Get your hands on this Limited Edition CD by following the details
listed below.
